Class CreatableResourcesImpl<T extends Resource,ImplT extends T,InnerT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.fluentcore.arm.collection.implementation.ReadableWrappersImpl<T,ImplT,InnerT>

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    SupportsBatchCreation<T>, SupportsDeleting
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupableResourcesImpl

    public abstract class CreatableResourcesImpl<T extends Resource,ImplT extends T,InnerT>
extends CreatableWrappersImpl<T,ImplT,InnerT>
implements SupportsBatchCreation<T>, SupportsDeleting
    Base class for creatable resource collection, i.e. those where the member of the collection is of Resource type Resource and are creatable. (Internal use only)
